➜要是有一天引力突然消失，你还有机会拉粑粑吗？
http://www.sohu.com/a/416070899_624188	13776
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200902/f75e24c3b747495ca9215609e4f00515.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每天早上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人类厕所会出现这一幕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200902/324f57b962074120bed206e7e2ec1ae0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为了给<strong>便秘</strong>找个高水平借口</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人人都成了<strong>物理学家</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要么赖地硬</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要么赖引力小</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200902/865643ada48c447e90a1ae6f83e29b7c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
