<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">——要是有一天引力突然消失了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">难不成你还省了拉粑粑的功夫？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">说到<strong>地球引力消失</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>顾城</strong>发挥想象力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直接写了首诗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200902/c8b0f531a1534fa39001a1508521e314.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">第一个问题来了——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200902/ce7cc3e28c5c45d292765d50aa1deb30.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200902/d89be8ee7d494bbc974f3021d3d1df12.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在说流星前</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我们复习一下<strong>引力</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200902/32a130a18d214f7fb86507dd1a7504ba.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">引力听起来没那么高大上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200902/22d8f2725de84f799b7b86aa7465c767.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你能脚踏实地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">全靠它</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你每次摔倒、抬起重物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都离不开它的帮忙</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>重力</strong>和<strong>向心力</strong>是引力的两个分力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">换句话说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只要有<strong>质量</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就难逃地球引力的作用</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都会被<strong>牢牢地束缚在地球上</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200902/8c2597327d2a477688f481cc00aa1b84.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>类</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>很</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>叛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>逆</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200902/7af7c30b3dbe49239cd1b5ba7f0d29d6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一听到引力消失</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">第一时间想到的就是<strong>飞起来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">像宇航员在太空一样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">仙气飘飘</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200902/22d8f2725de84f799b7b86aa7465c767.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">很抱歉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">宇航员在太空能飘起来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那叫<strong>失重</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">引力并没有消失！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">会出现这样的情况</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是<strong>因为宇航员随着飞行器一起绕地球高速旋转</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因此</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">地球对你的引力就<strong>只变成了向心力</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此时你四肢平时感受到的压力好像彻底消失一样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>相当于你的重力被偷走了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200902/41a2901dbe2142da88c26e19339463a6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当地球引力突然消失</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你就不是轻松飞起来那么简单</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相反</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">由于地球仍然在以<strong>466米每秒</strong>的速度快速自转</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你会跟地球一起转！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>像滚草一样沿着地球切线方向快速滚动！！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">何止你在滚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">周围的建筑、汽车、大树、高山、海水……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>都会疯狂地滚起来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200902/0ae96d3d69f04113a6afbcf89def17c6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">第二个问题来了——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200902/ce7cc3e28c5c45d292765d50aa1deb30.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">既然人类在快速地转</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>会不会转着转着</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>就成了顾城诗里的流星？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">别做梦了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你先骨鸽一下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>流星到底是什么——</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200902/2814b87c46ed4574b0458e4d5077837f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">流星是不可能了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">变成树根扎进土里更不可能了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">上面都说了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大树都滚起来了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">变成<strong>流星体</strong>还有点可能</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">——在惯性的作用下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我们的确会<strong>飞出地球</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200902/9f71087948aa4f4aaa9b5f0b966512c1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">第三个问题来了——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200902/562982d1fcc6430b9c43266fd23b6056.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你能顺利飞出地球吗？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">恭喜你</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>还是不能</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">需要提醒你的是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">失去引力后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你要考虑下<strong>地球的感受</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200902/69275972250a4b9e970f9806911887ba.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">——引力消失了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">意味着向心力也消失了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这时候唯一能维持地球不破裂的力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就只有<strong>矿物间的化学键</strong>了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也就是岩石的抗张强度</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">说白了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是如何让地壳不飞走的<strong>力</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">地壳多由<strong>长英质岩石</strong>构成</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">假定这根柱子是花岗岩的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有人专门算过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200902/e1deb2107369457a875cc4b34329756f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也就是说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果地球突然间失去了万有引力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">——<strong>地壳可能就要飞走了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就算地壳不飞走</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此时地心的巨大能量摆脱引力束缚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">地球内部不断高温</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可能会在几十分钟、几个小时或几天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将地球<strong>熔化</strong>或<strong>汽化</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">——<strong>地球最后会被引爆！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200902/93d241a1d6c24f24bd044276f492c622.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">说到这里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一切似乎离我们太遥远了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020年再怎么倒霉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也不会沦落到体验引力消失的终极倒霉事件</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个引力脑洞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都是源于<strong>牛顿被苹果砸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200902/65cb4dfdf41b4517ab1e8efc41a778d0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">说件更迷惑的事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200902/537756bf169445eca672d7d8a79ff3bd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牛顿传记作者<strong>大卫·布鲁斯特</strong>调查发现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>牛顿</strong>没有跟人提过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他最开始如何发现重力的故事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当然也就没有那颗落下的苹果</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只有牛顿的侄女<strong>凯瑟琳·巴顿</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">向<strong>伏尔泰</strong>提过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>1727年</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>牛顿去世</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牛顿与苹果的故事才出现在<strong>伏尔泰的回忆录</strong>里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牛顿的侄女反过来引用伏尔泰的版本</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">后来的科学史研究表明</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>牛顿发表的万有引力定律</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>其形成和发现是一个漫长的过程</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牛顿很可能受过<strong>胡克</strong>的重大影响</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200902/83b6d13aad4f47cfa9e611fc0f548364.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在现在看来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牛顿被苹果砸中发现万有引力的故事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更有<strong>传播效果</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还没等牛顿与苹果的故事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">推理出个真相</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>1915年</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>爱因斯坦</strong>提出了<strong>相对论</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">认为<strong>重力根本不是力</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直接把牛顿力学给扔了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他认为</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有一种看不见的基体叫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>时</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>空</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">时空遍及宇宙的每一个角落</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而物体的存在，扭曲了周遭的时空</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还改变了它的运动轨迹及其时间推移……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200902/e869df639b754e9a812c3f0f4ac6dd8f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">好吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">若你还是觉得不可思议</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">未来的事情还是交给未来吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">现在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你还是操心下<strong>与你和引力息息相关的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>痔</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>疮</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">痔疮的发生与痔内静脉循环不畅有关</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为地球引力的缘故</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>久坐</strong>或<strong>久站</strong>都会导致血液在痔内静脉淤积</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从而诱发痔疮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200902/51b95747161c457f90e15b570fd33a10.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200902/d73e258d60914c5e8fb4ece332a956b9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
